GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_SolutionArchetypes> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_SolutionArchetypes> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#SolutionArchetypes> ;
    narr:childCount "38"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "3ec7555c8f60b7b08de4d7e3f2696e6ab61154d5" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers solution archetypes, demo scripts, use-case taxonomies, and engagement playbooks. The most recent structural move (Jul 2, 2026) is a [Discovery / Onboarding / Governance three-way taxonomy](narr:Narrative_ThreeUseCaseTaxonomy) that explicitly demotes 'organizational memory' to a governance sub-use-case — sharpening an earlier (May 26) three-part frame of [governing a human team](narr:Narrative_UseCase1GoverningHumanTeam), [agentic steering at one-model and ecosystem scale](narr:Narrative_UseCase2AgenticSteering), and [steering the shared process across engagements](narr:Narrative_UseCase3SharedProcessSteering). A [collaboration-shape taxonomy](narr:Narrative_CollaborationTaxonomy) (Individual→Self/Team/Many, Team→Many) is flagged as the missing structural layer in the strategy doc. Onboarding methodology has its own arc: the [three-part seeding pattern](narr:Narrative_ThreePartSeedingPattern) (code-base review → topic analysis → ongoing iteration, May 1) was qualified by a [bulk-ingestion correction](narr:Narrative_BulkIngestionValidMethod) (May 21) and extended by a [hub-collection method at volume](narr:Narrative_HubCollectionMethodAtVolume) (Jul 5). Consulting delivery has evolved from [deck-as-derived-artifact](narr:Narrative_ConsultingModuleDeliverable) through a [three-phase engagement arc](narr:Narrative_EngagementArcThreePhase) (gift → backfill diagnostic → ongoing stream) to a [narrative-strategy report](narr:Narrative_NarrativeStrategyReport) as the most concrete fixed deliverable (Jun 30). Enterprise sales motion is anchored by [sponsor≠champion](narr:Narrative_SponsorVsChampionPlaybook) and [POC/MSA in parallel](narr:Narrative_POCMSAParallelism) (Tony, Apr 21). A [five-question discovery framework](narr:Narrative_FiveQuestionDiscoveryFramework) (Jul 15) doubles as call-one structure with a disqualification rule. Healthcare adds the [proposal artifact](narr:Narrative_ProposalArtifactPractitioner) lock-in framing (Apr 30).""" ;
